---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="AI Voice Receptionist for Dental, Chiropractic, Veterinary & Legal Practices | White AI Solutions"
  description="Your practice loses patients every time the phone goes unanswered. White AI Solutions installs a 24/7 AI voice receptionist that books appointments automatically. $347 setup for the first 5 clients."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-16 bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Layered background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-800"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/80 via-transparent to-slate-900/40"></div>
    <!-- Blue glow -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[400px] bg-blue-600/8 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <!-- Grain overlay -->
    <div class="grain-overlay"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 text-center">
      <p class="text-blue-400/90 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        AI Voice Receptionist &middot; Dental &middot; Chiro &middot; Vet &middot; Legal
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-6 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.35s;">
        Your Practice Loses Patients<br />
        Every Time the Phone<br />
        <span class="text-blue-400">Goes Unanswered.</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500 to-transparent mx-auto mb-6 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>

      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-300/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        30&ndash;35% of calls to dental and chiropractic practices go unanswered after hours. Each missed call is a patient who books with whoever picks up next.
      </p>

      <!-- Trust badge strip -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-2 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.58s;">
        <a href="#compliance" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-blue-500/40 bg-blue-950/50 text-blue-300 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-blue-400/60 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
          </svg>
          HIPAA Compliant
        </a>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-slate-600/50 bg-slate-800/50 text-slate-300 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
          </svg>
          SOC 2 Type II
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-slate-600/50 bg-slate-800/50 text-slate-300 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
          </svg>
          BAA Included
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.65s;">
        <a href="mailto:jadeofsapphire@gmail.com?subject=AI%20Voice%20Receptionist%20%E2%80%94%2015-Min%20Discovery%20Call" class="btn-primary text-white font-medium px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-sm tracking-wide">
          Book a Free 15-Minute Call
        </a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-outline !border-slate-600 !bg-slate-800/50 text-slate-200 font-medium px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-sm tracking-wide hover:!bg-slate-700/50 hover:!border-slate-500">
          See How It Works
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Live Demo Call Block -->
      <div class="mt-10 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
        <div class="inline-block border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/40 rounded-2xl px-8 py-6 text-center backdrop-blur-sm">
          <p class="text-blue-400/80 text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-3">Live Demo &mdash; Call Right Now</p>
          <a href="tel:+13853866852" class="block text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors tracking-tight leading-none">
            (385) 386-6852
          </a>
          <p class="text-slate-300/80 text-sm mt-3 font-light">This is the exact AI receptionist we install for your practice.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-2 tracking-wide">24/7 &middot; No app &middot; No signup &middot; Just call</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scroll indicator -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-slate-500">
          <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Scroll</span>
          <div class="w-px h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-500 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem / The cost of missed calls -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-offwhite">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">The Problem</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight">
          Every Missed Call Is a Patient<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Who Booked Somewhere Else
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 mt-12">
        <div class="reveal bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-blue-600 font-serif mb-4">30&ndash;35%</div>
          <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium mb-2">of calls go unanswered after hours, at lunch, and during busy periods.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">They're not calling back. They Googled your competitors while you were finishing with a patient, and someone else picked up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-serif mb-4">$0</div>
          <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium mb-2">revenue from a missed call. But the cost isn't just one appointment.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">A new dental patient is worth $800&ndash;$2,000+ over their lifetime. A missed call after 5pm on a Friday is real money gone.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 reveal">
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Your front desk can't work 24/7. Our AI receptionist can &mdash; answering every call, booking appointments, and handling FAQs around the clock.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section divider -->
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- What It Does -->
  <section id="services" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20 reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">What You Get</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-5">An AI Receptionist That<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Never Misses a Call</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">Works after hours, on weekends, during lunch, and whenever your front desk is occupied.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Answers Every Call, 24/7</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            After hours, weekends, lunch breaks, and whenever your staff is with a patient. No more voicemail jail for your callers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 9v7.5m-9-6h.008v.008H12V13.5zm0 3h.008v.008H12v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008H12v3zm3-6h.008v.008H15V13.5zm0 3h.008v.008H15v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008H15v3zm-6-6h.008v.008H9V13.5zm0 3h.008v.008H9v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008H9v3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Books Appointments Automatically</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Confirms, reschedules, and captures new patient information. Syncs with your existing scheduling system. Patients hang up with a confirmed time slot.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.625 9.75a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0h-.375m-13.5 3.01c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.087.16 2.185.283 3.293.369V21l4.184-4.183a1.14 1.14 0 01.778-.332 48.294 48.294 0 005.83-.498c1.585-.233 2.708-1.626 2.708-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0012 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Handles FAQs About Your Practice</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Hours, location, insurance accepted, what to expect at a first visit, pricing &mdash; trained on your specific practice. Sounds like a knowledgeable staff member.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4 -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-offwhite rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Routes Urgent Calls Immediately</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Dental emergencies, acute pain, urgent situations get transferred to the right person right away. Everything else is handled without interrupting your day.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 5 — full width -->
        <div class="reveal card-hover bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-100 md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Works on Your Existing Phone Number</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                No new hardware. No new numbers to advertise. No patient-facing changes at all. We configure it to work with your current line &mdash; patients call the same number they always have.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compliance & Security -->
  <section id="compliance" class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-900 to-slate-800"></div>
    <div class="grain-overlay"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-14 sm:mb-16 reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-400/90 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">Compliance &amp; Security</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-5">Built for Healthcare.<br class="hidden sm:block" /> HIPAA Compliant.</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">Patient data handled with the same rigor your practice requires. Not a workaround &mdash; full compliance baked in from the start.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="reveal bg-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700/50">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">HIPAA-Compliant Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Built on Retell AI, which is HIPAA compliant and SOC 2 Type II certified. Your patient call data is handled under verified, audited security controls.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal bg-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700/50">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">BAA Before Every Deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">We execute a Business Associate Agreement before going live with any healthcare practice. No shortcuts &mdash; compliance is in place before the first patient call.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal bg-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700/50">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Call Recordings Covered</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Call recordings and transcripts are covered under the BAA. Optional transcript PII removal available if your practice prefers zero stored PHI.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal bg-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700/50">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Never Used to Train AI</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Patient call data is never used to train AI models. Your patients&rsquo; conversations stay yours &mdash; they don&rsquo;t become someone else&rsquo;s training dataset.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-slate-600 text-xs mt-10 reveal">Powered by Retell AI &mdash; HIPAA compliant, SOC 2 Type II certified, Vanta verified.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section divider -->
  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-900 to-slate-800"></div>
    <div class="grain-overlay"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20 reveal">
        <p class="text-blue-400/90 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">Simple Process</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-5">Up and Running in Days,<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Not Weeks</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">No long contracts. No complicated software. Here's exactly how it works.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="reveal text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold step-number mb-4">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">15-Minute Discovery Call</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            We talk about your practice, your call volume, and what you're missing. I confirm the AI receptionist is the right fit. No cost, no commitment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="reveal text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold step-number mb-4">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">I Configure It for Your Practice</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            I train it on your hours, services, FAQs, and booking flow. We test it together before it touches a single patient call. Turnaround: 3&ndash;5 business days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="reveal text-center md:text-left">
